<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉y ḥml qd qblt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạảyã ḥim̊liⁿ qad̊ qabil̊ta
 rabãnā ạl̊fādī ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊
 biạkẖ̊tīāriⁿ qad̊ ạảṭaʿ̊ta
 fān̊ḥanay̱ ạlrãạ̊̉su ạl̊karīm̊

[V2]
 2- waj̊huka bāhī ạl̊jamāli
 faẘqahu ạldãmu ạl̊gẖazīr̊
 muf̊sadaⁿạ ṣāra lạảj̊lī
 ạảyũhā ạlrãbũ ạl̊qadīr̊

[V3]
 3- tayãạrātu ạllhi ʿajãt̊
 faẘqa rā̊̉sika ạl̊jalīl̊
 gẖaḍaba ạl̊ʿad̊li ḥamal̊ta
 ḥaẙtẖu ḥusib̊ta ạl̊badīl̊

[V4]
 4- mina ạllhi qad̊ turik̊ta
 was̊ṭa waḥ̊sẖaẗi ạlẓãlạam̊
 kulã daẙninā wafaẙta
 wamanaḥ̊tanā ạlsãlạam̊

[V5]
 5- yā ḥabība ạl̊qal̊bi ḥam̊daⁿạ
 lil̊kẖalạṣi wālrãjāʾ̊
 ʿan̊ qarībiⁿ sanakūnu
 maʿ̊ka fī maj̊di ạlsãmāʾ̊</lyrics>
<hymn_number>2072</hymn_number>
</song>